    {
      "type": "wokwi-text",
      "id": "text21",
      "top": 902.4,
      "left": -700.8,
      "attrs": {
        "text": "This part: Two \"registers\":\nSetting (IN0, IN1, IN2) to (0,1,1) stores (IN3,IN4,IN5,IN6) in \"register A\"\nSetting (IN0, IN1, IN2) to (1,1,0) stores (IN3, IN4, IN5, IN6) in \"register B\"\nSetting (IN0, IN1, IN2) to (1,1,1) shows either register A or register B\non (OUT4, OUT5, OUT6, OUT7), where IN7 selects between these registers.\nIN7=0: Show A, IN7=1: Show B"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "wokwi-text",
